PSCODE.display-label: Meaning of Products and services code
TVALLN: Total sales, receipts, or revenue of establishments with the product line ($1,000)
LINE_PCT: Sales, receipts, or revenue of product line as % of total sales, receipts, or revenue of estabs with the product line (%)
LINEALL_PCT: Sales, receipts, or revenue of product line as percent of total sales, receipts, or revenue of industry (%)
LINE_COV: Sales, receipts, or revenue of establishments reporting product lines as percent of total sales, receipts, or revenue (%)
KB_PCT: Broad line sls for industry as % of sector tot broad line sls (%)
